    "body": "Great find, this is due to:\r\n\r\n```go\r\nif len(req.Indices) == 0 && len(req.PublicKeys) == 0 {\r\n\t\t// return everything.\r\n\t\tfor i := 0; i < len(headState.Balances); i++ {\r\n\t\t\tres = append(res, &ethpb.ValidatorBalances_Balance{\r\n\t\t\t\tPublicKey: headState.Validators[i].PublicKey,\r\n\t\t\t\tIndex:     uint64(i),\r\n\t\t\t\tBalance:   balances[i],\r\n\t\t\t})\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\nin our ListValidatorBalances implementation. If the balances come from the archive, we shouldn't be appending to the `res` slice from `headState`, but rather from the archived balances. Will resolve this soon.",
